Name:          Nikola Tesla
Lived:         1856 - 1943
Nationality:   Serbian-American
Field:         Engineering
Known For:     AC electricity, induction motor
Contribution:  Alternating current power systems; Tesla coil; radio foundation
Quote:         "The present is theirs; the future is mine."

Name:          Ada Lovelace
Lived:         1815 - 1852
Nationality:   English
Field:         Computing
Known For:     First computer algorithm
Contribution:  Wrote first algorithm for Babbage's machine; recognized computing potential
Quote:         "The Analytical Engine weaves algebraic patterns."

Name:          Cleopatra VII
Lived:         69 - -30
Nationality:   Egyptian
Field:         Politics
Known For:     Last pharaoh of Egypt
Contribution:  Spoke 9 languages; allied with Caesar and Mark Antony; end of pharaonic era
